      "title": "[Boing Boing] Starlog returns in November after 17 years out of print",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Starlog-_2319.-Photo-_3Ca-href_3D_22https-www.flickr.jpg?fit=1080%2C802&amp;quality=60&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 0.75em;padding:5px 10px;background:#f0f4f8;border-left:3px solid #7b9fc4;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.82em;color:#444;line-height:1.8;\">🎨 🌾 🔧 🪶 🌲 🏔️ 🔭 <a href=\"https://zirnhelt.github.io/super-rss-feed/review.html?url=https%3A%2F%2Fboingboing.net%2F2026%2F07%2F02%2Fstarlog-returns-in-november-after-17-years-out-of-print.html\" style=\"color:#7b9fc4;text-decoration:none;\">✏️</a></p>\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Starlog-_2319.-Photo-_3Ca-href_3D_22https-www.flickr.jpg?fit=1080%2C802&amp;quality=60&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 0.75em;padding:5px 10px;background:#f0f4f8;border-left:3px solid #7b9fc4;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.82em;color:#444;line-height:1.8;\">🎨 🌾 🔧 🪶 🌲 🏔️ 🔭 <a href=\"https://zirnhelt.github.io/super-rss-feed/review.html?url=https%3A%2F%2Fboingboing.net%2F2026%2F07%2F02%2Fstarlog-returns-in-november-after-17-years-out-of-print.html\" style=\"color:#7b9fc4;text-decoration:none;\">✏️</a></p>\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Starlog-_2319.-Photo-_3Ca-href_3D_22https-www.flickr.jpg?fit=1080%2C802&amp;quality=60&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 0.75em;padding:5px 10px;background:#f0f4f8;border-left:3px solid #7b9fc4;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.82em;color:#444;line-height:1.8;\">🎨 🌾 🔧 🪶 <a href=\"https://zirnhelt.github.io/super-rss-feed/review.html?url=https%3A%2F%2Fboingboing.net%2F2026%2F07%2F02%2Fstarlog-returns-in-november-after-17-years-out-of-print.html\" style=\"color:#7b9fc4;text-decoration:none;\">✏️</a></p>\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Starlog-_2319.-Photo-_3Ca-href_3D_22https-www.flickr.jpg?fit=1080%2C802&amp;quality=60&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Starlog-_2319.-Photo-_3Ca-href_3D_22https-www.flickr.jpg?fit=1080%2C802&amp;quality=60&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Starlog-_2319.-Photo-_3Ca-href_3D_22https-www.flickr.jpg?fit=1080%2C802&amp;quality=60&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Starlog-_2319.-Photo-_3Ca-href_3D_22https-www.flickr.jpg?fit=1080%2C802&amp;quality=60&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<a href=\"https://boingboing.net/2026/07/02/starlog-returns-in-november-after-17-years-out-of-print.html\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Starlog returns in November after 17 years out of print\"><img alt=\"Starlog\" class=\"webfeedsFeaturedVisual wp-post-image\" height=\"802\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Starlog-_2319.-Photo-_3Ca-href_3D_22https-www.flickr.jpg?fit=1080%2C802&amp;quality=60&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto; margin-bottom: 5px;\" width=\"1080\" /></a><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Starlog, the science fiction magazine that ended its 33 year run in 2009, will <a href=\"https://starlog.com/\">return this fall</a> with a new print edition, a weekly podcast and a newsletter. And it will be edited by <a href=\"https://bsky.app/profile/annaleen.bsky.social\">Annalee Newitz!</a></p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">\"Fifty years ago, STARLOG went behind the scenes of alternate worlds for the first time.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p> &#8212; <a class=\"read-more\" href=\"https://boingboing.net/2026/07/02/starlog-returns-in-november-after-17-years-out-of-print.html\">Read the rest </a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://boingboing.net/2026/07/02/starlog-returns-in-november-after-17-years-out-of-print.html\">Starlog returns in November after 17 years out of print</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://boingboing.net\">Boing Boing</a>.</p>",
